metadata.name: The Beginning by Momo Pixel
metadata.description:
The Beginning by Momo Pixel

The Adventures of Momoland is a fantasy series that follows the mystical life of a runaway and her magical friends 
as she learns the truth about herself, the monsters of their world, and the secrets of the past while building the Kingdom of Momoland. 

With friends like Tobias, Loosha, and Rihleigh guiding and fighting along side her, will Momo succeed or forever be doomed to the 
evils of Oreamus.
